    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. This example utilizes the Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox, delivering power to the rear wheels via a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis has been properly maintained with rear subframe reinforcement and upgraded bushings to preserve torsional rigidity. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates within factory tolerances. The suspension geometry remains precise, providing the analog feedback and neutral handling balance characteristic of this platform. It presents in honest condition, ideal for the driver who prioritizes mechanical excellence and performance pedigree.",
